00:08:10.350 --> 00:08:15.500
If you look at any data set you're gonna
see a bunch of different patterns.

156
00:08:15.500 --> 00:08:16.880
Some of them are gonna be real.

157
00:08:16.880 --> 00:08:19.320
You would see them in
any similar data set.

158
00:08:19.320 --> 00:08:20.370
Some of them are not.

